	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">Calvin Klein 之前以为，他的简洁只适合美国女人</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-03-29 16:58:52 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-message">1</span>
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">25</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
